Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,Composing Message
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.79,0:00:05.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:08.90,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's a ton of chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.91,0:00:14.41,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai stayed up late \N last night, working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:17.50,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Today's Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:19.20,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:20.86,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:23.91,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning. You're up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:27.00,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I can't relax, so I \Nfigured I'd get going already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:28.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.78,0:00:30.75,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:33.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:35.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:43.45,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The day of Aoyama's audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:57.28,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:01:00.36,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,The artist we asked to \Ndo the cover is ill!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:04.57,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanohana Hall's popularity \Nis up recently, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:06.39,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so would you be able...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.39,0:01:08.68,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to work up a cover right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:09.29,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,In color.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:10.64,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Color?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:11.83,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, color.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.87,0:01:14.55,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Would yellow be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:15.66,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Yellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.66,0:01:17.98,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,A single color spread is \Ncertainly avant-garde, but no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.98,0:01:19.82,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cover! It's a challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:22.15,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,A challenge... Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:27.49,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I only tell her \NI'd see her later?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:31.16,Saku-main,SROATA,0000,0000,0000,,I should've sent her off with \Nsomething more helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:34.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina, it's time to get—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.34,0:01:40.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:42.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You got ready by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:44.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that the fashion now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:47.09,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sock, but I only found one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:49.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,They don't automatically \Nexist in pairs, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.66,0:01:54.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,And please don't tell me you've gone \Ncommando under that skirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:57.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you wearing panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:01:59.05,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,A very colorful pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:01.23,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to give me the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:03.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let me see what's in your bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:07.35,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Looking in a girl's bag is \Na horrible thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.28,0:02:10.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to \Ndo if you forget—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:12.14,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I have everything important.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:13.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "important"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:15.44,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I even packed my fighting spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.04,0:02:19.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're \Ntalking about, but whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:20.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I won't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:21.91,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You can look tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:24.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's different about tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:27.16,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Continuing to pry into her affairs \Nwould be very uncouth, Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:28.76,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Rita?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:31.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:34.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd contacted us, \Nwe'd have come to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:36.10,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't tell us you were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:36.97,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:39.26,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I've been busy with my work,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:41.34,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I forced some time off to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:48.33,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Today's Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.77,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,For girls, this day is a challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:51.77,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:56.80,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to stay and enjoy our reunion, \NMashiro, but it'll have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:03:00.20,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.69,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You won't escape, Ryunosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:08.54,Saku-overlap,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's the ex-freeloader doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:10.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we should head to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:11.37,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:13.96,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda! Kanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:13.96,Saku-overlap,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Ryunosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:45.54,Saku-main,STUDENTS,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:51.60,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}#17 Valentine's Day is Chocolate Day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:46.51,Saku-main,STUDENTS,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:53.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:56.94,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,To: Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:56.94,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:59.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama, you didn't go to your audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:02.00,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I can still make it if I go after class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:03.41,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to skip school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:04.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:05.03,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:11.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Um, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:12.30,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,About this morning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:17.85,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:22.63,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'm not expecting \Na great pep talk from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:27.36,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you've given me courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:27.21,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,To: Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:27.21,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:28.47,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Sending Message
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:28.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:29.37,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:33.72,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You proved that hard work is rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:35.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:38.82,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, do you remember our promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:39.94,Saku-main,AOYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:43.12,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You know, after the audition...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:45.44,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sorata and Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:46.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Miyahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:49.23,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the news. \NYou have an audition today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:50.43,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:52.49,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, Nanami, star of the \NGeneral Education Department!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:55.24,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Miyahara, you're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.06,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:04.09,Sign,BOARD,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.80,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,The word chocolate comes from the...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:10.13,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,indigenous Mexican word \N"xocolatl," meaning bitter water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:09.17,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Message Received{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:09.17,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mashiro
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.14,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}From: Shiina Mashiro{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.14,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}No Subject{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.14,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting on the roof after school for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:11.74,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,So, listen up, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:14.36,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give chocolate to the one you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:13.50,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:15.19,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.76,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Even if you claim that you're \Nconveying sweet feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:16.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:19.14,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}it's originally bitter water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.65,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:23.15,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I have everything important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:27.44,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Whose idea was it to write "chocolate" with \Nkanji meaning "sugar growing old"? Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:27.14,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Was Shiina going to give me chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:28.95,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Give up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:33.61,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, I'd expect men to \Ncry tears of joy if a girl as cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:36.20,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,as me was this determined to pursue them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:40.05,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Ryunosuke, what don't you like about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:41.68,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:43.70,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'll make sure you take my chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.21,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm telling you I {\i1}won't{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:50.23,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,If I accept one of your demands, \Nwho knows what you'll ask for next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:52.45,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't paint me as some kind of terrorist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:54.52,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,That's {\i1}exactly{\i0} what you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:56.85,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,On Christmas Eve...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.53,0:07:02.72,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I was really happy to get an \Nemail from you, but was that—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:05.85,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a New Year's card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:08.18,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese are conscientious people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:09.15,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:12.24,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:22.77,Saku-main,KOHARU,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:25.55,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:27.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:29.36,Saku-overlap,GIRL A,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, you're on \Ncleaning duty, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:30.28,Saku-main,GIRL A,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:30.99,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:31.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:32.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:33.34,Saku-main,GIRL A,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hop to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:39.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,They work me like a dog at \NSakura Hall and at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:42.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.11,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:46.60,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:47.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:50.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Is that for Jin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:51.43,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:54.31,Saku-main,HAUHAU,0000,0000,0000,,Third years can come \Nand go as they please,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:56.91,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but Soichiro-kun promised to bring him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:07:58.49,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The Student Council President?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.92,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's why we're waiting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:04.15,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you making all kinds of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.96,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's a pretty small chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:07.61,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What?! This isn't good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:08.92,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It won't convey my love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:11.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, actually, this one looks \Nmore like you're serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to him, Misaki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:19.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:20.67,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:25.73,Saku-main,HAUHAU,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki, you've got a good kouhai there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:28.26,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's the best kouhai-kun ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:36.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:41.00,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Shiina's waiting up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.92,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Incoming Call{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.92,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama Nanami
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.14,0:08:47.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:49.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.25,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do, Kanda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.51,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done for! I'm screwed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:54.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, what—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.98,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,The train! It's stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:57.41,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,They're saying there was an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:08:59.76,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,They don't know when it'll get \Ngoing again! I'm done for—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:02.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Have you contacted the training school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:04.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,They'll understand if you explain \Nthe situation to them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:07.92,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I told them, and they said they \Ncould push back my audition, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.58,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,they said it had to be today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:13.36,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't get there by six, \Nall the other auditions will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama, which station \Nare you at right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.74,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What? At the next one over...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:19.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get out of the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:21.53,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm calling you from the platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:23.85,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Then, wait for me outside the ticket gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:25.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina, sorry! I'm going \Nto be a little late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:34.38,Saku-main,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The number you are trying to \Nreach is currently unavailable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:37.38,Saku-main,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please leave a message after the tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:40.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.85,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:43.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold out here, so wait in a classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:53.94,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:55.12,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:57.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Miyahara, let me borrow your bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:58.07,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama's train isn't running!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:02.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Her audition is today and \Nshe's stuck at the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:03.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:05.16,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:06.25,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:07.46,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:09.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Miyahara? You could just lend it to—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.17,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Just get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:13.58,Saku-main,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two! Riding double isn't allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:15.10,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come back so you \Ncan yell at us later,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:16.38,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so just let it slide for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:18.97,Saku-main,TEACHER,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:35.69,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Miyahara, let's switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:38.22,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:42.39,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Understand the power of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:42.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,"Of love"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:50.87,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at my limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.89,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,You take over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:54.76,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Go by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:56.68,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Miyahara. What did you \Nmean by the power of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:57.54,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Correction:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:00.40,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of a loser's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:03.01,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami rejected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:05.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:08.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean she rejected... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:08.09,Saku-overlap,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:09.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:16.02,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Ride like the wind, Sorata!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:23.58,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,The one Nanami called \Nwhen she was in trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.33,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:39.80,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:43.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama, let's hurry and get a taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:45.78,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,We can't. Everyone else is getting taxis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:46.97,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be any for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:48.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:50.53,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What? We'll never make \Nit in time on a bike—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:52.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You've work hard for the last \Ntwo years, haven't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:57.23,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We said we'd work hard together... \NPursue our dreams together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:12:01.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you quit here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:02.88,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:06.08,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Take me there, Kanda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:07.87,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to the audition hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.81,Saku-thought,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for my flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:41.82,Saku-thought,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I really didn't have the time to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:45.34,Saku-thought,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanted to at least see you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:51.38,Saku-thought,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell the other \Nresidents of Sakura Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:53.47,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,that I'm sorry I couldn't tell them goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.76,0:12:56.82,Saku-thought,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Mashiro I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:12:59.92,Saku-thought,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,P.S.,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:02.49,Saku-thought,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Our kiss at the airport...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:05.91,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,was my first kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.76,0:13:17.01,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he didn't come after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:20.59,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you wait in \Nthe cold with me, Hau-hau.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:22.32,Saku-main,HAUHAU,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. You don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:26.45,Saku-main,HAUHAU,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try calling Soichiro-kun \Nand get him to call Mitaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:28.50,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.12,Saku-main,HAUHAU,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:32.20,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have plenty of other \Nchances to go after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:36.18,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I'll buy you a bun to \Nthank you for staying with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:38.17,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You can have a pork bun, a red \Nbean bun, or even a pizza bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:42.23,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's bun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:45.56,Saku-main,HAUHAU,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.34,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Bun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:01.07,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,This has happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:07.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:08.86,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to practice your script?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:11.23,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:14.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're riding a bike, \Nit's harder for us to hear each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:17.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to speak up, so it'll be good\N for practicing your projection, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:23.74,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, you're always so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:27.20,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:28.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:32.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what did you want \Nto talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:35.43,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually pretty important, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:40.50,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,He's always so close to my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:44.40,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,There's actually something I've \Nalways wanted to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:45.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:46.74,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:50.20,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:53.25,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I've always... always...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:04.31,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I've always loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:08.53,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:17.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama. I, u-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.13,0:15:21.41,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,How was that? Was it believable?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:24.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. You surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:28.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right. There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:33.01,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,This is close enough. \NI think I'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:35.64,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kanda-kun. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:40.08,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:45.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina's still waiting for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:50.70,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:53.31,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,My legs feel so weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:57.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,One last spurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:16:01.64,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If she's still waiting for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:05.28,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Today is Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:07.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:14.04,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She left already...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:36.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:38.25,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You always break your promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:39.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:42.89,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,When it's just the two \Nof us, call me Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.28,0:16:45.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:46.69,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:48.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bamboo shoots?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:51.40,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine's Day is chocolate day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:55.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:59.11,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But you could've waited until \Nwe got back to Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.37,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to do it normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Normally?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:05.55,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,There were lots of girls giving \Ntheir chocolate to guys on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.71,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Even in the manga Ayano gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:12.03,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:15.38,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I haven't \Nunderstood you recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:16.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:18.31,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:20.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,F-Far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:21.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:23.68,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You get along well with Yuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's because she's my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.50,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what about Nanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:28.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:31.98,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You went to Nanami's side today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:34.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Today's an important day for Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:39.70,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It was an important day for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:45.62,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't say to me that \Nwe'd work hard together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:47.15,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:49.12,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're already a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:50.59,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're leagues ahead of...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:55.98,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:18:00.91,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina's always been \Nrunning way ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:05.89,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's so far ahead, \NI can't even see her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:11.50,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not the only one who can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.91,0:18:14.74,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If Shiina looks back,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:17.45,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,she can't see me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:26.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking forward to this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:28.06,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:31.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might give \Nme some chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:34.68,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,After I received your text during class,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:36.51,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't wait for school to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:39.59,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Does the chocolate \Nmake you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:41.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The bamboo shoots are my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:43.47,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.01,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:48.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't want you to \Ncatch cold. Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:49.38,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:51.95,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Can I hold your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:06.25,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:07.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:08.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:09.71,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:12.01,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Because it makes me feel uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:14.13,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,My heart is pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:16.90,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:23.26,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:27.27,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:31.77,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:36.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Your heart is pounding \Nbecause you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:38.01,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:43.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I feel even more alive than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:13.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:15.62,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.28,0:21:18.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama, you're back already?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:20.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How did your audition go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:21.38,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:24.01,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I think I did everything I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:26.56,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:29.35,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai said we're having \Na Valentine's pot sticker party.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:31.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why pot stickers on Valentine's Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:36.56,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,She even forced Akasaka-kun \Nto help her wrap them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:37.88,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:41.23,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Rita?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:42.40,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Rita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:46.99,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,The ex-freeloader went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:48.45,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:50.12,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Rittan was here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:52.25,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you stop her \Nfrom leaving, Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:54.75,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed busy. Not much I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:57.42,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But she came all the way to Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.79,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Something happened, \Ndidn't it, Akasaka-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:11.06,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose everyone \Nhas a secret or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.40,0:22:16.01,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I'm sure Rittan \Nwill be back again real soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.54,0:22:18.40,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:21.04,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat some delicious food!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:25.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.77,0:22:26.94,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:29.69,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she managed to give \Nher chocolate to Jin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.95,0:22:31.10,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,She might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.82,0:22:33.62,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how close \Nyou are to someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:35.75,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,there are some things \Nyou just can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:37.24,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.89,0:22:39.67,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing Aoyama said this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.22,0:22:43.00,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, do you remember our promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:47.90,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,If I pass my audition, I want you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:52.60,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,to listen to what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:54.60,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:22:59.38,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kanda-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.38,0:23:00.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.15,0:23:03.37,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up. I'm reading \N too much into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.83,0:23:06.84,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama couldn't possibly \Nfeel that way about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:08.65,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:10.20,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It should be one or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:13.49,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet or salty...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.93,0:23:15.44,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It should be one or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.04,0:23:17.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate pot stickers?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.81,0:23:20.50,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiron, you got the lucky one!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:23.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't your mother tell you \Nnot to play with your food?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.77,0:23:25.28,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,There's even garlic in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.28,0:23:26.27,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.27,0:23:27.02,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't taste very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:29.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you meant by \NValentine's pot stickers?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:32.86,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We're aliens!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.86,0:23:34.88,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,In space, there are lots of twinkling stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.87,0:23:40.98,NextEptitle,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,#18 First Love with an Alien
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.88,0:23:36.15,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,And then, there's dark matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.15,0:23:38.15,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,An inexpressible and terrifying feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.15,0:23:40.98,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think I'm sparkling right now?
